{"tid":1813540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【修例風波】新學期開學 段崇智冀中大如鳳凰般浴火重生","createTime":"2020-01-06T10:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T12:03:07.000Z","uid":64694,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"786344d7eda8dd3a823fd25ef715938c982a147e","tid":1813540,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjFigZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjFigZy.jpg&h=869228c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n段崇智（小圖）指自己會親自領導多項跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n因應今日是中文大學2019至20年度第二學期的開學日，<span style=\"color: red;\">中大段崇智今日發出公開信，指近月大學經歷幾許風雨，但他相信這些考驗和困難只會使大家更加團結及堅定，如鳳凰般浴火重生。</span>他又指，自己會親自領導多項跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n段崇智表示，除修繕基礎設施，眼前更大的挑戰是重建大學成員、夥伴及不同持分者之間的信任，而他會親自領導多項跟進工作。早前成立的跨部門迅速應變專責工作組的5個分組，將繼續密切跟進及完善涵蓋學業支援、文化共融、學生身心健康和校園保安等各項政策及措施，聆聽不同的看法和意見。<br />\n<br />\n段崇智指出，為安全起見，現時大學出入仍受管制，個別地點如二號橋和夏鼎基運動場將繼續關閉。除此之外，校園往來大致暢通亦適宜居住。鑑於大量校巴於11月被毀壞，校方安排臨時校巴穿梭校園；港鐵大學站則局部開放。開學初期，難免有少許不便，他請各方多加體諒，予校園空間修復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1674660/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8-%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E5%86%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A6%82%E9%B3%B3%E5%87%B0%E8%88%AC%E6%B5%B4%E7%81%AB%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1674660%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2586%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E8%2588%25AC%25E6%25B5%25B4%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=c8d642e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1674660%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2586%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E8%2588%25AC%25E6%25B5%25B4%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F&h=1083c2fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1674660/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8-%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E5%86%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A6%82%E9%B3%B3%E5%87%B0%E8%88%AC%E6%B5%B4%E7%81%AB%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如鳳凰般浴火重生</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n段校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfaa73da76206ad3077b528f82692d79de631e0","tid":1813540,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8e37db4124fe33370ed5319ecfa8dbe88ea0e69","tid":1813540,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"原來龍津美食係支那人開，唔怪之食完成日肚痛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fafac7de8203027bbb11edc7afcfe5eaff943e8f","tid":1813540,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"500e166d3832057a109a618d97ba5dfe737fcfc1","tid":1813540,"uid":251945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"香港一大校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p