.000Z","msg":"屌我都第一時間諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e19c25320cab4f9a57a5beb0c3b4ab5ffa73be9","tid":1813540,"uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81150eafd3081269429dcd9242e849b5598be1c9","tid":1813540,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fafac7de8203027bbb11edc7afcfe5eaff943e8f","tid":1813540,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"屌我都第一時間諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"2007年，年僅14歲的女神童何凱琳在會考中獲9優1良佳績，獲中文大學錄取修讀理科、通識及語文等課程，第二年入讀中大醫學院，成為醫學院最年輕學生。何凱琳在7歲已被確定為資優兒童，IQ達130以上。她當年在網誌自稱Physics Phoenix，故有「物理鳳凰」的外號。<br />\n<br />\n2011年，何凱琳本應升讀醫科四年級，不過三年級到威爾斯親王醫院進行內外科實習後，發覺自己真正志趣不在醫科，而是心理學，故轉系並在一年級重新開始學習。"},{"pid":"92551efcbd95cf4ad4f5517bbc073e264f78a835","tid":1813540,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac043d43f3443ce7d603916199afce32460bd9d7","tid":1813540,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"段爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0d75e8bc04668e35854a690eb19872e168b6de","tid":1813540,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e19c25320cab4f9a57a5beb0c3b4ab5ffa73be9","tid":1813540,"uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81150eafd3081269429dcd9242e849b5598be1c9","tid":1813540,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fafac7de8203027bbb11edc7afcfe5eaff943e8f","tid":1813540,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"屌我都第一時間諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"rep